Description: Docker Container Vulnerability Scanner for Astra Linux
 A comprehensive security scanner for Docker containers,
 specifically designed for Astra Linux 1.7.6 environments.
 Features include:
  * Local and remote container scanning
  * Web interface for easy management
  * Integration with Trivy scanner
  * Real-time vulnerability checking
  * Detailed security reports 